gcloud auth application-default login = Connect your SDK with the console

gcloud auth 


terraform = Checks the availability of terraform in the system environment 

terraform -v = Checks the version of the terraform

touch nameofthefile.tf = creates a terraform file for writing code

terraform init = This will initialize various local settings and data, mostly updates the provider and the plug in

terraform plan = check whether the execution plan for a set of changes matches your expectations without making any changes to real resources or to the state.

terraform apply = Apply the changes made in the terraform file

terraform show = Inspect the current state of config

terraform destroy = Destroy the infrastructure or resource

